'''Allianz De Architecture''' is an architecture, design and planning firm that was founded in 2001 in [[Mumbai, India]]. It currently operates offices in Mumbai and [[Bangalore]] in [[India]] and provides urban design and architectural consulting and planning services. The firm's designs can be seen at various parts of Mumbai and nearby metropolitan regions and it is known for its work inspired by sustainable modern architectural practices as well as a sensitivity for society and the built-natural environment.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adaarchitects.co.in|title=Allianz De Architecture - Design & Liasoning Consultants|work=adaarchitects.co.in|accessdate=23 May 2015}}</ref>

==History==
The firm was established in 2001 by Suresh L. Hulikal as a proprietary firm and Since its inception in the year 2001, this vibrant and promising organization has been committed to serve the industry with the finest way of ideating and fastest way of working. This firm has taken creativity to the next level of crafting and contemporary architectural design. From a modest beginning, till date, the firm have come a long way.  Over the years, this firm has built several landmarks

== People ==
'''Suresh L. Hulikal''', principal architect at Mumbai office served the firm with the best of his knowledge and have created skylines influencing many great architects in the country.

'''Fakhruddin Bhanpurawala''', Former Assistant Architect contributed in firm with the best of skills and have been on the award-winning category in the firm. He was designated as Assistant architect and coordinator at allianz de architecture, Mumbai office.

