'''Supervizion''' is a business consulting firm founded in 1986 that provide [[Talent manager|artist management]], [[management consulting]] and [[creative services]].
The firm is active in the music industry and other creative industries. Supervizion has been involved in record production within [[electronic dance music]] and [[Hip hop music|rap music]].<ref>{{cite web|last=discogs.com|title=Joel Mull Retrospectives |url=http://www.discogs.com/Joel-Mull-Retrospectives/release/26011|accessdate=28 March 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=discogs.com|title=021 Represent: Westaroze Hiphop Compilation |url=http://www.discogs.com/Various-021-Represent-Westaroze-Hiphop-Compilation/release/2920573|accessdate=28 March 2016}}</ref> Supervizion's creative work has been displayed during [[Fashion week|Fashion Week]] in Stockholm, the show was broadcast in northern Europe by the TV channel [[Star! Scandinavia|Star!]].<ref> {{cite news | last = | first = | title = Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week Stockholm S/S 2012 | newspaper = Bon Magazine | location = | pages = | language = | publisher = | date = 2012-08-11 | url =http://bon.se/film/mercedes-benz-fashion-week-stockholm-ss-2012/jennifer-blom/ | accessdate =2016-03-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=youtube.com|title=Stockholm Fashion Week on Star! |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vTRmJV7aGy4|accessdate=28 March 2016}}</ref>
